; Coverage test for account.cc miscellaneous lookup functions.
; Exercises 'l' shorthand for depth (L455-456), is_account returning
; true (L448-449), is_index/subcount (L450-451, L482-484),
; account_base (L409-410), addr (L411-412), and use_direct_amount
; (L492-494). Also covers latest_cleared (L457-458).

2024/01/01 * Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 * Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --no-total --format "%(l)|%(is_account)|%(is_index)|%(subcount)|%(account_base)|%(account)\n"
2|true|3|3|Cash|Assets:Cash
1|true|0|0|Expenses|Expenses
2|true|2|2|Food|Expenses:Food
2|true|1|1|Gas|Expenses:Gas
end test
